---
to: "k8s/service.yaml"
description: "Generate Kubernetes Service manifest for exposing deployments"
category: config
requires:
  - app_name
  - service_type
variables:
  app_name: "Application name"
  service_type: "Service type (ClusterIP, NodePort, LoadBalancer)"
  port: "Service port (default: 80)"
  target_port: "Container port to forward to (default: 8080)"
  selector: "Label selector (default: app={app_name})"
mode: overwrite



---







apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: {{ app_name | lower }}
  labels:
    app: {{ app_name | lower }}
spec:
  type: {{ service_type | default("ClusterIP") }}
  selector:
    app: {{ selector | default(app_name | lower) }}
  ports:
  - name: http
    protocol: TCP
    port: {{ port | default(80) }}
    targetPort: {{ target_port | default(8080) }}
{% if service_type == "NodePort" %}
    nodePort: {{ node_port | default(30080) }}
{% endif %}
{% if service_type == "LoadBalancer" %}
  loadBalancerIP: {{ load_balancer_ip | default("") }}
{% endif %}
  sessionAffinity: ClientIP
  sessionAffinityConfig:
    clientIP:
      timeoutSeconds: {{ session_timeout | default(10800) }}

## Signal Theory

**Signal**: `S=(linguistic, configuration, inform, yaml, k8s-service)`
- **Mode**: linguistic
- **Genre**: configuration
- **Type**: inform
- **Format**: yaml
- **Structure**: k8s-service

## Usage

```bash
# Apply service
kubectl apply -f k8s/service.yaml

# Get service URL
minikube service {{ app_name | lower }} --url

# Get service info
kubectl describe service {{ app_name | lower }}

# Port forward to local
kubectl port-forward service/{{ app_name | lower }} 8080:80
```

## Service Types

### ClusterIP (default)
- Internal cluster access only
- Stable IP within cluster
- Use for backend services

### NodePort
- External access via node IP + port
- Port range: 30000-32767
- Use for development/testing

### LoadBalancer
- External load balancer (cloud provider)
- Assigns public IP
- Use for production external access

### Ingress (alternative)
For HTTP/HTTPS routing with Ingress controller:

```yaml
apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata:
  name: {{ app_name | lower }}
spec:
  rules:
  - host: {{ app_name | lower }}.example.com
    http:
      paths:
      - path: /
        pathType: Prefix
        backend:
          service:
            name: {{ app_name | lower }}
            port:
              number: 80
```
